function teamStats(gameId='ALL',half='ALL',seasonId='ALL'){return statsFrom(scopeRows(data.shots,{gameId,half,seasonId}),scopeRows(data.freeThrows,{gameId,half,seasonId}),scopeRows(data.events,{gameId,half,seasonId}),scopeRows(data.lineupStints,{gameId,half,seasonId}),null,null,gameId,half)}
function playerStats(player,gameId='ALL',half='ALL',seasonId='ALL'){const shots=scopeRows(data.shots,{gameId,half,player,seasonId}),fts=scopeRows(data.freeThrows,{gameId,half,player,seasonId}),events=scopeRows(data.events,{gameId,half,player,seasonId}),lines=scopeRows(data.lineupStints,{gameId,half,seasonId}).filter(l=>[l.player_1,l.player_2,l.player_3,l.player_4,l.player_5].includes(player));return statsFrom(shots,fts,events,lines,scopeRows(data.shots,{gameId,half,seasonId}),player,gameId,half)}
function lineupsStats(gameId='ALL',half='ALL',seasonId='ALL'){const m=new Map();scopeRows(data.lineupStints,{gameId,half,seasonId}).forEach(l=>{const label=l.lineup_label||[l.player_1,l.player_2,l.player_3,l.player_4,l.player_5].filter(Boolean).join(' / ');if(!m.has(label))m.set(label,{lineup_label:label,stints:0,points_for:0,points_against:0,off_poss:0,def_poss:0});const r=m.get(label);r.stints++;r.points_for+=num(l.points_for);r.points_against+=num(l.points_against);r.off_poss+=num(l.off_poss);r.def_poss+=num(l.def_poss)});return [...m.values()].map(r=>{r.net_points=r.points_for-r.points_against;r.off_rating=safe(r.points_for*100,r.off_poss);r.def_rating=safe(r.points_against*100,r.def_poss);r.net_rating=(r.off_rating!==null&&r.def_rating!==null)?r.off_rating-r.def_rating:null;return r}).sort((a,b)=>b.net_points-a.net_points)}
function breakdown(shots,key,buckets){return buckets.map(b=>{const r=shots.filter(s=>String(s[key]||'')===b),fga=r.length,fgm=r.filter(made).length,pts=shotPoints(r);return{label:b,FGM:fgm,FGA:fga,FG_pct:safe(fgm,fga),rate:safe(fga,shots.length),PTS:pts,PPS:safe(pts,fga)}})}
function eventBreakdown(events){const map=new Map();(events||[]).forEach(e=>{const key=(e.event_type||'')+'||'+(e.event_subtype||'');if(!map.has(key))map.set(key,{type:e.event_type||'',subtype:e.event_subtype||'',count:0,pts:0});const r=map.get(key);r.count+=rowCount(e);r.pts+=num(e.points_created)});return Array.from(map.values()).sort((a,b)=>b.count-a.count||String(a.type).localeCompare(String(b.type)))}
function kpis(el,items){el.innerHTML=items.map(([label,val,type])=>`<div class="kpi"><div class="label">${esc(label)}</div><div class="value">${type==='pct'?pct(val):fmt(val)}</div></div>`).join('')}
function statRows(rows){return '<table class="stat-table"><tbody>'+rows.map(([a,b,t])=>`<tr><td>${esc(a)}</td><td>${t==='pct'?pct(b):fmt(b)}</td></tr>`).join('')+'</tbody></table>'}

function signed(v){if(v==null||v==='')return '—';const n=Number(v);if(!Number.isFinite(n))return fmt(v);return (n>0?'+':'')+fmt(n)}
function gameRecord(gameId){return (data.games||[]).find(g=>String(g.game_id)===String(gameId))||{}}
function playersForReport(gameId='ALL',half='ALL',seasonId='ALL'){return playerNames().map(n=>playerStats(n,gameId,half,seasonId)).map(s=>({...s,Creation_Value:num(s.AST)+num(s.Potential_AST)+num(s.Adv_Created)+num(s.Drive_Kick_3PA_Created),Def_Activity:num(s.STL)+num(s.BLK)+num(s.DEFLECTION)+num(s.Charges_Drawn)}))}
function topStat(players,key,min=1){const rows=players.filter(p=>num(p[key])>=min).sort((a,b)=>num(b[key])-num(a[key]));return rows[0]||null}
function leaderCard(title,row,key,labelFn=null){if(!row)return `<div class="leader-card"><div class="label">${esc(title)}</div><div class="name">—</div><div class="value">No data yet</div></div>`;const value=labelFn?labelFn(row):fmt(row[key]);return `<div class="leader-card"><div class="label">${esc(title)}</div><div class="name">${esc(row.player)}</div><div class="value">${esc(value)}</div></div>`}
function heatColor(fg){if(fg>=0.5)return '#2f7d4f';if(fg>=0.35)return '#d4a437';return '#b8392b'}
function zoneHeatCells(shots){const rows=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',ZONES);const byZone=Object.fromEntries(rows.map(r=>[r.label,r]));const size=0.5;let out='';for(let y=0;y<14;y+=size){for(let x=0;x<15;x+=size){const z=zoneFromXY((x+size/2)/15*100,(y+size/2)/14*100).zone;const r=byZone[z];if(!r||!r.FGA)continue;out+=`<rect class="zone-heat" x="${x.toFixed(2)}" y="${y.toFixed(2)}" width="${size}" height="${size}" fill="${heatColor(r.FG_pct)}" opacity="0.18"/>`}}return out}

function toggleRegionOverlay(){state.showRegionLabels=!state.showRegionLabels;saveState();renderReports()}
function updateRegionOverlayToggle(){const btn=q('regionOverlayToggle');if(!btn)return;btn.textContent=state.showRegionLabels?'Hide region labels':'Show region labels';btn.classList.toggle('active',!!state.showRegionLabels)}
const ZONE_LABEL_POS={'rim':[7.5,1.05],'paint':[7.5,3.9],'left midrange':[3.4,6.85],'middle midrange':[7.5,6.85],'right midrange':[11.6,6.85],'left corner 3':[1.65,1.15],'right corner 3':[13.35,1.15],'left wing 3':[2.45,5.9],'right wing 3':[12.55,5.9],'top 3':[7.5,10.9],'other':[7.5,13.15]};
function regionLabelsSvg(shots){if(!state.showRegionLabels)return '';return breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',ZONES).filter(r=>r.FGA>0).map(r=>{const p=ZONE_LABEL_POS[r.label]||[7.5,13.15];const w=Math.max(2.80,Math.min(4.35,String(r.label).length*.22+1.45));const h=.98;const x=Math.min(Math.max(p[0]-w/2,0.10),15-w-0.10);const y=Math.min(Math.max(p[1]-h/2,0.10),14-h-0.10);const cx=x+w/2;return `<g class="region-label"><rect x="${x.toFixed(2)}" y="${y.toFixed(2)}" width="${w.toFixed(2)}" height="${h}" rx="0.16"/><text class="zone-name" x="${cx.toFixed(2)}" y="${(y+0.38).toFixed(2)}">${esc(r.label)}</text><text class="zone-stats" x="${cx.toFixed(2)}" y="${(y+0.72).toFixed(2)}">${r.FGM}/${r.FGA} · ${pct(r.FG_pct)}</text></g>`}).join('')}
function lineupImpactCards(gameId,half,seasonId){const rows=lineupsStats(gameId,half,seasonId);if(!rows.length)return '<div class="lineup-impact-card"><div class="label">Lineup impact</div><div class="lineup-name">No lineup stints match these filters yet.</div><div class="sub">Track lineup stints to see best/worst groups, net rating, and plus-minus.</div></div>';const bestNet=rows.slice().sort((a,b)=>num(b.net_points)-num(a.net_points))[0];const worstNet=rows.slice().sort((a,b)=>num(a.net_points)-num(b.net_points))[0];const bestRtg=rows.slice().filter(r=>r.off_poss||r.def_poss).sort((a,b)=>num(b.net_rating)-num(a.net_rating))[0]||bestNet;const card=(label,r,value,sub)=>`<div class="lineup-impact-card"><div class="label">${esc(label)}</div><div class="lineup-name">${esc(r?.lineup_label||'—')}</div><div class="value">${value}</div><div class="sub">${sub}</div></div>`;return [card('Best plus-minus lineup',bestNet,signed(bestNet.net_points),`PF ${bestNet.points_for} · PA ${bestNet.points_against} · ${bestNet.stints} stint${bestNet.stints===1?'':'s'}`),card('Worst plus-minus lineup',worstNet,signed(worstNet.net_points),`PF ${worstNet.points_for} · PA ${worstNet.points_against} · ${worstNet.stints} stint${worstNet.stints===1?'':'s'}`),card('Best net rating lineup',bestRtg,signed(bestRtg.net_rating),`Off ${fmt(bestRtg.off_rating)} · Def ${fmt(bestRtg.def_rating)} · Off poss ${bestRtg.off_poss}`)].join('')}

function bestZoneText(shots){const rows=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',ZONES).filter(r=>r.FGA>0).sort((a,b)=>num(b.PPS)-num(a.PPS));if(!rows.length)return 'No shot data yet.';const best=rows[0];return `${best.label}: ${best.FGM}/${best.FGA}, ${fmt(best.PPS)} PPS`}

function attentionCutoffs(half){const full=String(half||'ALL')==='ALL';return{full,turnovers:full?10:5,turnoversMajor:full?14:7,threePA:full?12:6,threePAHigh:full?18:9,fga:full?35:18,openFGA:full?10:5,lightFGA:full?10:5,badFGA:full?8:4,zoneFGA:full?3:2,misses:full?20:10,fta:full?6:3}}
function weaknessZoneText(shots){const rows=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',ZONES).filter(r=>r.FGA>=2).sort((a,b)=>num(a.PPS)-num(b.PPS));if(!rows.length)return 'Need more attempts to flag a cold zone.';const cold=rows[0];return `${cold.label}: ${cold.FGM}/${cold.FGA}, ${fmt(cold.PPS)} PPS`}
function attentionItems(t,shots,events,fts,half='ALL'){
  const c=attentionCutoffs(half),items=[];
  const add=(title,msg,priority=1)=>items.push({title,msg,priority});
  const pctText=v=>pct(v);
  const fgText=(m,a)=>`${fmt(m)}/${fmt(a)}`;
  const threePct=t.threeP_pct, fgPct=t.FG_pct;
  const tov=countEvents(events,'turnover'),poss=num(t.Poss_Used),tovRate=safe(tov,poss);
  const misses=Math.max(0,num(t.FGA)-num(t.FGM)),orbRate=safe(num(t.OREB),misses);
  if(t.threePA>=c.threePA && threePct!==null && threePct<.30){
    const vol=t.threePA>=c.threePAHigh?'very high volume':'high volume';
    add('3PT shooting',`3PT shooting was ${fgText(t.threePM,t.threePA)} (${pctText(threePct)}) on ${vol}.`,5);
  }
  if(t.FGA>=c.fga && fgPct!==null && fgPct<.38){
    add('Overall efficiency',`Overall FG was ${fgText(t.FGM,t.FGA)} (${pctText(fgPct)}).`,4);
  }
  if(tov>=c.turnovers || (tov>=Math.max(6,c.turnovers-2) && tovRate!==null && tovRate>=.16)){
    const severity=tov>=c.turnoversMajor?'major':'worth flagging';
    add('Turnovers',`Turnovers: ${fmt(tov)}${tovRate!==null?` (${pctText(tovRate)} of used possessions)`:''}. For 2×20 halves, ${c.turnovers}+ is ${severity}.`,4);
  }
  const openPct=safe(t.Open_FGM,t.Open_FGA), lightPct=safe(t.Light_Contest_FGM,t.Light_Contest_FGA);
  if(t.Open_FGA>=c.openFGA && openPct!==null && openPct<.40){
    add('Open-shot conversion',`Open looks were ${fgText(t.Open_FGM,t.Open_FGA)} (${pctText(openPct)}), ${fmt(t.Open_PPS)} PPS.`,3);
  }
  if(t.Light_Contest_FGA>=c.lightFGA && lightPct!==null && lightPct<.35){
    add('Light-contest conversion',`Light-contest shots were ${fgText(t.Light_Contest_FGM,t.Light_Contest_FGA)} (${pctText(lightPct)}), ${fmt(t.Light_Contest_PPS)} PPS.`,2);
  }
  if(t.Bad_Shot_FGA>=c.badFGA && t.Bad_Shot_Rate!==null && t.Bad_Shot_Rate>=.20){
    add('Bad-shot diet',`Bad shots were ${fgText(t.Bad_Shot_FGM,t.Bad_Shot_FGA)} and made up ${pctText(t.Bad_Shot_Rate)} of attempts.`,3);
  }
  if(t.FTA>=c.fta && t.FT_pct!==null && t.FT_pct<.65){
    add('Free throws',`Free throws were ${fgText(t.FTM,t.FTA)} (${pctText(t.FT_pct)}).`,2);
  }
  if(misses>=c.misses && orbRate!==null && orbRate<.15){
    add('Offensive glass',`Only ${fmt(t.OREB)} OREB on ${fmt(misses)} missed shots (${pctText(orbRate)}).`,2);
  }
  const zones=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',ZONES).filter(r=>r.FGA>=c.zoneFGA && ((r.FG_pct!==null&&r.FG_pct<.30)||(r.PPS!==null&&r.PPS<.75))).sort((a,b)=>(b.FGA-a.FGA)||(num(a.PPS)-num(b.PPS))).slice(0,3);
  if(zones.length){
    add('Cold zones',zones.map(r=>`${r.label} ${r.FGM}/${r.FGA} (${pctText(r.FG_pct)}, ${fmt(r.PPS)} PPS)`).join('; '),2);
  }
  const paint=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',['paint'])[0],rim=breakdown(shots,'shot_zone',['rim'])[0];
  if(paint&&paint.FGA>=5&&paint.FG_pct!==null&&paint.FG_pct<.45){
    add('Paint finishing',`Paint shots were ${paint.FGM}/${paint.FGA} (${pctText(paint.FG_pct)}).`,3);
  }else if(rim&&rim.FGA>=5&&rim.FG_pct!==null&&rim.FG_pct<.60){
    add('Rim finishing',`Rim shots were ${rim.FGM}/${rim.FGA} (${pctText(rim.FG_pct)}).`,3);
  }
  items.sort((a,b)=>b.priority-a.priority);
  return items;
}
function needsAttentionHtml(t,shots,events,fts,half='ALL'){
  const items=attentionItems(t,shots,events,fts,half);
  if(!items.length)return '<span>No major red flags from the current report thresholds.</span>';
  return `<ul class="attention-list">${items.slice(0,7).map(i=>`<li><b>${esc(i.title)}:</b> ${esc(i.msg)}</li>`).join('')}</ul>`;
}
function buildGameReportHero(gameId,half,t,players,seasonId='ALL'){const g=gameRecord(gameId),isAll=gameId==='ALL';const result=(g.result||'').toLowerCase();const teamScore=t.PTS || g.team_score || 0;const oppScore=g.opponent_score ?? '—';const opp=isAll?'All games':(g.opponent?`vs ${g.opponent}`:'Selected game');const shots=scopeRows(data.shots,{gameId,half,seasonId});const events=scopeRows(data.events,{gameId,half,seasonId});const fts=scopeRows(data.freeThrows,{gameId,half,seasonId});const scoreMain=isAll?`<div class="score-main"><span class="num">${esc(teamScore)}</span><span class="unit">PTS</span></div>`:`<div class="score-main score-pair"><span class="num">${esc(teamScore)}</span><span class="dash">–</span><span class="num">${esc(oppScore)}</span></div>`;const leaders=[leaderCard('Top scorer',topStat(players,'PTS'), 'PTS',r=>`${r.PTS} pts`),leaderCard('Top creator',topStat(players,'Creation_Value'), 'Creation_Value',r=>`${r.Creation_Value} creation actions`),leaderCard('Best screener',topStat(players,'Screen_Created_Total'), 'Screen_Created_Total',r=>`${r.Screen_Created_Total} screen-created`),leaderCard('Top rebounder',topStat(players,'REB'), 'REB',r=>`${r.REB} reb`),leaderCard('Defensive activity',topStat(players,'Def_Activity'), 'Def_Activity',r=>`${r.Def_Activity} plays`)].join('');return `<div class="report-hero"><div><div class="section-kicker">Game report</div><h1 class="report-title">${esc(isAll?(seasonId==='ALL'?'All seasons / all games':seasonId+' / all games'):gameId+' '+opp)}</h1><div class="report-meta"><span>${esc(half==='ALL'?'All halves':half)}</span>${!isAll&&g.date?`<span>${esc(g.date)}</span>`:''}<span class="badge ${result==='w'?'w':result==='l'?'l':'neutral'}">${esc(g.result||'report')}</span></div><div class="leader-grid">${leaders}</div></div><div class="score-box"><div><div class="label">${esc(isAll?'Total points':'Score')}</div>${scoreMain}<div class="small muted score-sub">FG ${t.FGM}/${t.FGA} · 3PT ${t.threePM}/${t.threePA} · FT ${t.FTM}/${t.FTA}</div></div></div></div><div class="report-note-grid"><div class="report-note"><b>Shot quality</b>Open shot rate ${pct(t.Open_FGA_Rate)} · Light contest rate ${pct(t.Light_Contest_Rate)} · Bad shot rate ${pct(t.Bad_Shot_Rate)} · Assisted FG rate ${pct(t.Assisted_FG_Rate)}</div><div class="report-note"><b>Best zone</b>${esc(bestZoneText(shots))}</div><div class="report-note needs-attention"><b>Needs attention</b>${needsAttentionHtml(t,shots,events,fts,half)}</div></div>`}

function gameStoryCards(t,players){const bestCreator=topStat(players,'Creation_Value'),bestScreen=topStat(players,'Screen_Created_Total'),bestDef=topStat(players,'Def_Activity');return `<div class="story-card"><div class="label">Efficiency</div><div class="main">${fmt(t.PTS)} pts · ${pct(t.eFG_pct)} eFG</div><div class="sub">FG ${t.FGM}/${t.FGA}, 3PT ${t.threePM}/${t.threePA}, FT ${t.FTM}/${t.FTA}, TS ${pct(t.TS_pct)}</div></div><div class="story-card"><div class="label">Shot quality</div><div class="main">${pct(t.Open_FGA_Rate)} open · ${pct(t.Light_Contest_Rate)} light · ${pct(t.Bad_Shot_Rate)} bad</div><div class="sub">Open ${t.Open_FGM}/${t.Open_FGA}, light ${t.Light_Contest_FGM}/${t.Light_Contest_FGA}, bad ${t.Bad_Shot_FGM}/${t.Bad_Shot_FGA}</div></div><div class="story-card"><div class="label">Creation + screening</div><div class="main">${t.AST} AST · ${t.Screen_Created_Total} screens</div><div class="sub">Extra potential AST ${t.Potential_AST}, advantage created ${t.Adv_Created}. ${bestCreator?`Top creator: ${esc(bestCreator.player)}.`:''} ${bestScreen?`Best screener: ${esc(bestScreen.player)}.`:''}</div></div><div class="story-card"><div class="label">Possession battle</div><div class="main">${t.TOV} TOV · ${t.REB} REB</div><div class="sub">OREB ${t.OREB}, DREB ${t.DREB}, defensive activity ${t.Defensive_Playmaking}. ${bestDef?`Activity leader: ${esc(bestDef.player)}.`:''}</div></div>`}

function ensureReportNotes(){data.reportNotes=data.reportNotes||{}}
function reportNotesKey(gameId,half){return `${gameId||'ALL'}|${half||'ALL'}`}
function renderReportNotes(gameId,half){const el=q('reportNotesInput');if(!el)return;ensureReportNotes();const val=data.reportNotes[reportNotesKey(gameId,half)]||'';el.value=val;el.textContent=val}
function saveReportNotes(){const el=q('reportNotesInput');if(!el)return;const gameId=q('report_game')?.value||'ALL',half=q('report_half')?.value||'ALL';ensureReportNotes();data.reportNotes[reportNotesKey(gameId,half)]=el.value;el.textContent=el.value;saveData(true);q('saveState').textContent='Saved report notes '+new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}
function controlDashboardHtml(t){
  const ftr=safe(t.FTA,t.FGA),tovRate=safe(t.TOV,t.Poss_Used),rebTotal=t.REB||0;
  const card=(label,main,sub)=>`<div class="control-card"><div class="label">${esc(label)}</div><div class="main">${main}</div><div class="sub">${sub}</div></div>`;
  return [
    card('Shooting',`${pct(t.eFG_pct)} <span class="unit">eFG</span>`,`${t.FGM}/${t.FGA} FG · ${t.threePM}/${t.threePA} 3PT · ${pct(t.TS_pct)} TS`),
    card('Shot quality',`${pct(t.Open_FGA_Rate)} <span class="unit">open</span>`,`${pct(t.Light_Contest_Rate)} light · ${pct(t.Bad_Shot_Rate)} bad · ${pct(t.Assisted_FG_Rate)} assisted FG`),
    card('Possessions',`${fmt(t.PTS_per_Poss)} <span class="unit">PTS/Poss</span>`,`${fmt(t.Poss_Used)} used · ${pct(tovRate)} TOV/use · ${fmt(t.AST_TO)} AST/TO`),
    card('Glass / Def Activity',`${rebTotal} <span class="unit">REB</span>`,`${t.OREB} OREB · ${t.DREB} DREB · ${t.Defensive_Playmaking} def activity · FTr ${pct(ftr)}`)
  ].join('')
}
function halfSplitsHtml(gameId,seasonId='ALL'){
  const halves=['1H','2H','OT'];
  const rows=halves.map(h=>({h,s:teamStats(gameId,h,seasonId)})).filter(r=>r.s.PTS||r.s.FGA||r.s.FTA||r.s.AST||r.s.TOV||r.s.REB||r.s.Fouls||r.s.STL||r.s.BLK);
  if(!rows.length)return '<tr><td colspan="14" class="muted">No half split data for this filter yet.</td></tr>';
  return rows.map(r=>`<tr><td>${esc(r.h)}</td><td class="num">${r.s.PTS}</td><td class="num">${splitStatCell(r.s.FGM,r.s.FGA,r.s.FG_pct)}</td><td class="num">${splitStatCell(r.s.threePM,r.s.threePA,r.s.threeP_pct)}</td><td class="num">${splitStatCell(r.s.FTM,r.s.FTA,r.s.FT_pct)}</td><td class="num">${pct(r.s.TS_pct)}</td><td class="num">${r.s.AST}</td><td class="num">${r.s.TOV}</td><td class="num">${r.s.Fouls}</td><td class="num">${r.s.OREB}</td><td class="num">${r.s.DREB}</td><td class="num">${r.s.STL}</td><td class="num">${r.s.BLK}</td><td class="num">${pct(r.s.Bad_Shot_Rate)}</td></tr>`).join('')
}
function creationLeadersHtml(players){const rows=players.slice().sort((a,b)=>(b.AST+b.Potential_AST+b.Adv_Created)-(a.AST+a.Potential_AST+a.Adv_Created));if(!rows.length)return '<tr><td colspan="9" class="muted">No player data.</td></tr>';return rows.map(s=>`<tr><td>${esc(s.player||'')}</td><td class="num">${s.AST}</td><td class="num">${s.AST_PTS}</td><td class="num">${s.Potential_AST}</td><td class="num">${s.Adv_Created}</td><td class="num">${s.Adv_Created_PTS}</td><td class="num">${s.Paint_Touches_Created}</td><td class="num">${s.Drive_Kick_3PA_Created}</td><td class="num">${fmt(s.AST_TO)}</td></tr>`).join('')}
function screenLeadersHtml(players){const rows=players.slice().sort((a,b)=>b.Screen_Created_Total-a.Screen_Created_Total);if(!rows.length)return '<tr><td colspan="7" class="muted">No player data.</td></tr>';return rows.map(s=>`<tr><td>${esc(s.player||'')}</td><td class="num">${s.Screen_AST}</td><td class="num">${s.Screen_Created_Opp}</td><td class="num">${s.Screen_Adv}</td><td class="num">${s.Screen_Created_Total}</td><td class="num">${s.Screen_Created_PTS}</td><td class="num">${fmt(s.PTS_per_Screen_Created)}</td></tr>`).join('')}
function scoringLeadersHtml(players){const rows=players.slice().filter(s=>num(s.PTS)||num(s.FGA)||num(s.FTA)).sort((a,b)=>num(b.PTS)-num(a.PTS)||num(b.eFG_pct)-num(a.eFG_pct));if(!rows.length)return '<tr><td colspan="9" class="muted">No player data.</td></tr>';return rows.map(s=>`<tr><td>${esc(s.player||'')}</td><td class="num">${s.PTS}</td><td class="num">${s.FGM}/${s.FGA} (${pct(s.FG_pct)})</td><td class="num">${s.threePM}/${s.threePA} (${pct(s.threeP_pct)})</td><td class="num">${s.FTM}/${s.FTA}</td><td class="num">${pct(s.eFG_pct)}</td><td class="num">${pct(s.TS_pct)}</td><td class="num">${fmt(s.PTS_per_Poss)}</td><td class="num">${pct(s.Usage_pct)}</td></tr>`).join('')}
